{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-244-sliders","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 244: Listovi","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možda ste upoznati sa igrom Fifteen Puzzle. Ovde, umesto pločica sa brojevima, imamo sedam belih pločica i osam plavih pločica.</p>\n<p>Igra je prikazana velikim slovom pravca (Levo, Desno, Gore, Dole) gde se taster pomera, na primer počevši od stanja ($S$), sa sekvencom $LULUR$ dolazimo do stanja ($E$):</p>\n<p>($S$) <img alt=\"configuration S\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/sliders-1.gif\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: white; padding: 10px;\">, ($E$) <img alt=\"configuration E\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/sliders-2.gif\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: white; padding: 10px;\"></p>\n<p>Za svaki način, kontrolna suma (checksum) se računa pomoću (placeholder koda):</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; \\text{checksum} = 0 \\\\\n&#x26; \\text{checksum} = (\\text{checksum} × 243 + m_1) \\; \\text{mod} \\; 100\\,000\\,007 \\\\\n&#x26; \\text{checksum} = (\\text{checksum} × 243 + m_2) \\; \\text{mod} \\; 100\\,000\\,007 \\\\\n&#x26; \\ldots \\\\\n&#x26; \\text{checksum} = (\\text{checksum} × 243 + m_n) \\; \\text{mod} \\; 100\\,000\\,007\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>gde $m_k$ je ASCII vrednost k-tog karaktera u sekvenci koraka, a ASCII vrednosti za korake su:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{array}{|c|c|}\n\\hline\nLevi &#x26; 76 \\\\ \\hline\nDesni &#x26; 82 \\\\ \\hline\nGore &#x26; 85 \\\\ \\hline\nDolje &#x26; 68 \\\\ \\hline\n\\end{array}$$</p>\n<p>Za niz $LULUR$ prikazan iznad, checksum će biti 19761398. Sada, počevši od pozicije ($S$), pronađi sve najkraće staze za dolazak do pozicije ($T$).</p>\n<p>($S$) <img alt=\"configuration S\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/sliders-3.gif\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: white; padding: 10px;\">, ($T$) <img alt=\"configuration T\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/sliders-4.gif\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: white; padding: 10px;\"></p>\n<p>Koji je zbir svih checksum vrednosti najkraćih putanja?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4601000cf542c50ff72","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301891,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-244-sliders"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function sliders() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nsliders();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>sliders()</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>96356848</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sliders(), 96356848);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-244-sliders","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-245-coresilience","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-243-resilience","id":"5900f4601000cf542c50ff72","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["